summary:
maknae line 「a reporter bad-mouthed you」
Scenario
After walking down the red carpet, the boys were interviewed by the local TV...
body:
maknae line 「a reporter bad-mouthed you」

Scenario

After walking down the red carpet, the boys were interviewed by the local TV reporters. Numbers of questions were asked and many; numerous of them were about you. Approximately a week ago, the boys had agreed that it was the right time to revealed your relationship, as you and your boyfriend have been dating for quite a while and the company has also agreed to that. It surprised you when the reactions are more positive than what you have thought.

Everything was going very well until one of the reporter asked very specific questions of you to your boyfriend. You were watching the red carpet behind your TV screen and knew that the interview will not lead to anything good, and it turned out you were more than right.

Jimin

Jimin was smiling sweetly to the camera when he heard your name from the reporter’s lips. He concentrated even more on the conversation from that point.

“So, Jimin-shi, army is now very crazy about the news of you dating, what do you think about the reaction thought?”

“It was so positive, I couldn’t believe it myself either.”

“But have you heard rumor circulating around about y/n? They say that people saw her around a pub?”

You almost choked on your popcorn when you heard that. Going to a pub? You barely go out of your room.

“I have nothing to say about that.” You liked how calmly Jimin could answer that question. It was the right answer though, not confirming anything.

“So, are you saying it was true?” The moment that question left the lips of the reporter, you swear you could see Yoongi’s hand holding Jimin’s.

“Is it, Jimin-shi?” Jimin looked down on his shoes, probably contemplating whether he should reply him or not.

“Maybe the company can answer you later, but what I am sure about is that now, she is eating popcorn at home instead of meeting people,” he answered with a smile before the boys said their parting statement and were leaded inside the venue.

Taehyung

Taehyung was happier than you when he received the news that army’s reaction were more positive than negative. He knew he’ll be getting many questions about you as this was his first public appearance since the announcement. All the questions have been amazing and Taehyung were more than glad to be abled to answer all of them.

You were also checking all the updates from twitter as you need to stay longer at your workplace to finish all your works. Procrastination. You read through all the tweets under the trending hastags and found a live broadcast.

“Taehyung, what make you choose her?”

“Excuse me?” Taehyung quickly answered.

“I know many of your fans are very happy about the statement but still, you couldn’t deny that some donot.”

“I know. That’s why I want to show them that there are more of y/n to love.”

“What if people cannot see that? I personally belong to the other side of the group. Many said that you could have bett-“

Taehyung was smiling at the reporter when he cut him mid-sentence, “Then you shouldn’t have come and interviewed us.”

“Please respect people,” Namjoon added to the offensive reporter and went to the next one.

Jungkook

Jungkook is usually the quiet one during an interview, but he decided that he will answer many questions this time since he knew most of them will be directly aimed at him.

It shook you when he suddenly showed up at your place last week to tell you that he wanted to make the relationship public. You hesitated for a moment but agreed to him regardless. When you know army loves you just as much as they love Jungkook, you were glad you made that decision.

You saw how Jungkook nailed every questions in the interviews, he really matured a lot since the day you met him. It was at that one particular question that you really knew you’ve been dating the right man.

“So, do you mind telling army out there what kind of girl is y/n?”

“Hmm, she’s just like all other human out there. Except she is more humane than anyone I know. She loves Autumn Leaves so much sometimes Yoongi hyung brags.” His answer made everyone chuckled.

“Apart from that?” Is there anything you dislike from her?”

“Dislike?”

“Yes. We all have never seen her in real life, is she perhaps way shorter than you? or is she a worker or a student? Have you ever think of anyone that might suit you better?

Namjoon almost replied to the question but Jungkook did instead.

“Physical traits are just trait. It does not make me love her any less. What she is doing now is also up to her and I respect that, no matter what she did, I trusted her.”

The reporter and the other boys were left dumbfound by Jungkook’s answer, only learning that it was not the end of his reply.

“And no, she suits me, best.”

“Hmm, she’s just like all other human out there. Except she is more humane than anyone I know. She loves Autumn Leaves so much sometimes Yoongi hyung brags.” His answer made everyone chuckled.

“Apart from that?” Is there anything you dislike from her?”

“Dislike?”

“Yes. We all have never seen her in real life, is she perhaps way shorter than you? or is she a worker or a student? Have you ever think of anyone that might suit you better?

Namjoon almost replied to the question but Jungkook did instead.

“Physical traits are just trait. It does not make me love her any less. What she is doing now is also up to her and I respect that, no matter what she did, I trusted her.”

The reporter and the other boys were left dumbfound by Jungkook’s answer, only learning that it was not the end of his reply.

“And no, she suits me, best.”
